Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.23,0:00:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.88,0:00:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  我来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.74,0:00:27.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苏菲小姐…已经进去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.35,0:02:33.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  这怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.45,0:02:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.57,0:02:36.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这  这个行李箱突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:41.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.20,0:02:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞西尔老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:44.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久城同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.53,0:02:46.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦  为什么会在行李箱里面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有危险啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.68,0:02:51.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为教师不能看着学生身处危险不管
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.91,0:02:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是拼死的潜入调查
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.22,0:02:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静一下  学生是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.72,0:02:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了  维多利加同学有危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.79,0:03:04.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维多利加同学又被爸爸叫出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.63,0:03:12.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就待在这里  塞西尔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.72,0:03:15.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再靠近了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:20.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉和平时的样子不太一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.64,0:03:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我在行李箱里也不太清…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:27.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久城同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.59,0:03:36.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.50,0:03:40.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  借过——
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:44.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
